headline: Hidden Valley® Ranch Picks Up Checked Bag Fees for Labor Day Travelers Who Pack the Flavor
summary: This Labor Day Weekend, Hidden Valley Ranch is making travel tastier, and a lot easier, by covering checked bag fees for fans who bring their favorite ranch along for the ride.
